TITLE: Initializing Forest Admin Agent with Koa Application
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to initialize the Forest Admin agent with a Koa application. It creates a new agent, adds a datasource, and starts the agent with the Koa app.
SOURCE: https://github.com/forestadmin/agent-nodejs/blob/main/packages/datasource-mongo/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

